WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: uz

00:00:00.006 --> 00:00:04.389
Salom, Jessika.

00:00:04.389 --> 00:00:05.870
Salom, Katerina.

00:00:05.870 --> 00:00:08.090
Men Andredan mana bu eskizlarni oldim, 
ularni tekshirib ko‘rishni xohlaysizmi?

00:00:08.090 --> 00:00:08.590
Albatta.

00:00:09.890 --> 00:00:10.930
Nima deb o‘ylaysiz?

00:00:10.930 --> 00:00:12.910
Vov, ular rostdan ham yaxshiga 
o‘xshab ko‘rinayapti.

00:00:12.910 --> 00:00:13.700
Ha.

00:00:13.700 --> 00:00:16.149
Demak, menga bularning 
hammasi yoqayapti.

00:00:16.149 --> 00:00:17.781
Ammo, balki biz bu yerda birinchisidan 
foydalanmasligimiz kerakdir.

00:00:17.781 --> 00:00:19.140
Nima uchun?
Xo‘sh, Android da, 

00:00:19.140 --> 00:00:21.216
umuman olganda biz chayqalib turuvchi 
oynalarni ishlatishni yoqtirmaymiz, 

00:00:21.216 --> 00:00:23.342
uning o‘rniga biz to‘g‘ridan-to‘g‘ri ilovaning 
tarkibiy qismiga o‘tamiz, shunda, 

00:00:23.342 --> 00:00:26.327
foydalanuvchi chayqaluvchi ekranni 
yuklanishini kutib o‘tirishi kerak bo‘lmaydi.

00:00:26.327 --> 00:00:27.489
Yaxshi, buni qanday qilib bildingiz?

00:00:27.489 --> 00:00:29.329
Xo‘sh, bu material dizayn yo‘riqnomasida berilgan.

00:00:29.329 --> 00:00:32.439
Ha, Kanola va men bu narsani o‘tgan 
kursda to‘liq o‘rganganmiz.

00:00:32.439 --> 00:00:35.615
Talabalar bu spec ni 
oldindan ortga deb bilishadi.

00:00:35.615 --> 00:00:39.430
Ammo, spec ni bilish uni 
qo‘llashdan boshqacha.

00:00:39.430 --> 00:00:42.430
Shunday qilib, biz rostdan ham dizayn 
uchun ozroq yordam olsak bo‘lardi.

00:00:42.430 --> 00:00:43.900
Aslida, men sizni shu yergacha olib 
kelganingizdan xusandman.

00:00:43.900 --> 00:00:46.360
Demak, men bu ajoyib dizaynerlar jamoasini bilaman.

00:00:46.360 --> 00:00:47.520
Ular bizning fikrlarimizni, biz xohlagan 
xususiyatlarni qabul qila oladi, 

00:00:47.520 --> 00:00:50.330
va biz uchun ba’zi bir chiroyli 
namunalar yaratib bera oladi.

00:00:50.330 --> 00:00:51.300
Bu ajoyib eshitilyapti.

00:00:51.300 --> 00:00:53.640
Ha, demak, men bu eskizlarni ularga 
olib borsam qanday bo‘ladi.

00:00:53.640 --> 00:00:54.860
Yaxshi.
Men ba’zi namunalarni qaytarib olaman va 

00:00:54.860 --> 00:00:55.683
siz bilan keyinroq ko‘rishaman.

00:00:55.683 --> 00:00:56.566
Yaxshi, rahmat.

00:00:56.566 --> 00:00:57.270
Hammasi yaxshi, ko‘rishguncha.

00:00:58.350 --> 00:00:59.470
Demak, siz ilovani birinchi ochganingizda, 

00:00:59.470 --> 00:01:04.849
biz sonlar, oila a’zolari, ranglar va 
jumlalar kategoriyalarining ro‘yxatini ko‘ramiz.

00:01:04.849 --> 00:01:09.210
Agar siz sonlar kategoriyasi ustiga 
bossangiz, u sonlar ro‘yxatini ko‘rsatadi.

00:01:09.210 --> 00:01:13.245
Va birinchisi uchun bizda ingliz va 
miwok so‘zlari bor, 

00:01:13.245 --> 00:01:17.953
shuningdek, bitta rasm va miwok talaffuzini 
baland ovozda chiqrib beradigan tugmacha ham bor.

00:01:17.953 --> 00:01:22.520
Va oila, ranglar va jumlalar kategoriyalari 
uchun ham bir xil shunday qo‘llaniladi.

00:01:22.520 --> 00:01:26.320
Demak, masalan, ismingiz nima va 
o‘zingizni qanday his qilayapsiz

00:01:26.320 --> 00:01:29.020
kabi jumlalar uchun rostdan ham ularni yonida 
qo‘yish uchun ularni tasvirlaydigan rasm mavjud emas.

00:01:29.020 --> 00:01:31.480
Natijada, biz inglizcha va miwok cha 
tarjimalarni ovozni ijro etib beradigan

00:01:31.480 --> 00:01:34.770
variantda qilishga qaror qildik.

